===Intransitive verb===
{{en-infl-reg-other-e|resolv|e}}

# To make a firm decision to do something.
#:''I '''resolve''' to finish this work before I go home.''

====Translations====
*Chinese: [[决定]] (jueding), [[决心]] (juexin)
*French: se [[résoudre]]
*Hungarian: [[elhatároz]]
*Japanese: [[決定する]] (けっていする, kettei-suru), [[決心する]] (けっしんする, kessin-suru)

